{"tid":2107063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[投反對票都違國安法]政府指號召否決預算案或違國安法　戴耀廷：屬立法會憲制權力","createTime":"2020-07-13T15:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T15:39:58.000Z","uid":105567,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7a2e18fa00be3865447142beea113a08d209eb21","tid":2107063,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T15:32:53.000Z","msg":"民主派初選今晚 (13 日) 公布初步結果，而政制及內地事務局亦於相約時間發聲明，指收到投訴，初選的主辦單位號召「35+」，否決財政預算案以達到「攬炒」目的，認為該等行為涉違反《港區國安法》，特首林鄭月娥在出席防疫措施記者會時，亦提出類似說法。有份協調初選的港大法律學系副教授戴耀廷說，政府的聲明有事實錯誤，主辦單位從無作出任何號召，亦無在任何聲明中提及過「攬炒」。他又說，否決財政預算案是《基本法》賦予立法會的權利，不明白為何是「非法手段」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E5%88%9D%E9%81%B8-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8C%87%E8%99%9F%E5%8F%AC%E5%90%A6%E6%B1%BA%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E6%88%96%E9%81%95%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E6%88%B4%E8%80%80%E5%BB%B7-%E5%B1%AC%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E6%86%B2%E5%88%B6%E6%AC%8A%E5%8A%9B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%2588%259D%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2599%259F%25E5%258F%25AC%25E5%2590%25A6%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25A1%2588%25E6%2588%2596%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E6%2588%25B4%25E8%2580%2580%25E5%25BB%25B7-%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2586%25B2%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%258A%259B%2F&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCn8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=c3f233e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%2588%259D%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2599%259F%25E5%258F%25AC%25E5%2590%25A6%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25A1%2588%25E6%2588%2596%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E6%2588%25B4%25E8%2580%25